Package edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.frontend

Interface Summary
StatusUpdater  
 

Class Summary
AnalysisController Master controller of analysis routines.
DataSummary Summarizes the output from analysis routines, combining all output from a directory into a single unified file.
DirUtils Utilities for getting files from a directory or OMERO data source and matching them together into sets of the different channels of the same image.
IJAnalysis Interface to run analysis routines from an ImageJ plugin.
ImageAnalysisToolsPlugin_ An implementation of the ImageJ PlugIn interface that allows the user to select a parameters file and run analysis on the currently displayed ImagePlus.
ImageJStatusUpdater  
LocalAnalysis Controls analysis done on the local machine, including routines for threading analysis, and data input and output.
LoggingStatusUpdater  
LoggingUtilities Wraps a logging system to provide simple methods for all classes in the imageanalysistools package to get a uniform logger, control its level of logging detail, and add handlers.
MaximumIntensityProjection Utilities for creating maximum intensity projections of images.
